visual.name: Drill_Down_Timeline_PRO_By_ZoomCharts
visual.displayName: Drill Down Timeline PRO (Filter) by ZoomCharts
visual.description: Drill Down Timeline PRO (Filter) takes its foundation from Drill Down TimeSeries PRO (Filter), and lets you explore time-based data using DAX calculated measures. Additional features and improvements allow for a unique type of time series visualization and time axis customization. Click directly on the time chart to drill down to examine specific periods in detail. Combine multiple series and choose between multiple chart types (line, column, area).
